<arggraph id="micro_c008" topic_id="older_people_better_parents" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[I think it's possible for older people to be better parents.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[They have had time to mature more and learn about themselves.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[They're more likely to have steady careers going]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[so they can provide for a child.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Some might say being too old risks the child being disabled,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[but insisting all babies be perfect is demanding the impossible]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[as well as demeaning to people already living who are disabled.]]></edu>
